author: crogers
msg: Fix for http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEEHIVE-1049 - NetUI's internal CompilerUtils.getClassMethods() will sometimes include duplicate methods.

Minor change to make sure the for loop breaks once we find that we already have a method override (same name and parameters) and don't add the inherited (duplicate) method. Also minor clean up of the test, InheritOverloadedActions.
tests: bvt in netui, including compiler tests (WinXP)
